metadata.title: data.norge.no - SPARQL sandbox
metadata.description: Explore and query Norwegian public data using SPARQL. Execute custom queries on datasets, concepts, APIs, and information models from over 125 organizations. Test your SPARQL queries in our interactive sandbox environment.

title: SPARQL sandbox
description: Execute SPARQL queries to search and explore Norwegian public data. Query datasets, concepts, APIs, and information models from over 125 organizations. Test and refine your queries in this interactive environment.
